title: Bloomberg Markets 12/12/2025
description: "Bloomberg Markets" follows the market moves across every global asset class and discusses the biggest issues for Wall Street. Today's guests: BitGo Co-Founder and CEO Mike Belshe, Bloomberg's Ed Ludlow, Keith Naughton, Dave Lee and Poonam Goyal. (Source: Bloomberg)
